description: The Orange Is the New Black actor grew up the daughter of Nigerian immigrants in a predominantly white Massachusetts suburb. She looks back on her mother's influence in the memoir, The Road Is Good.
title: Uzo Aduba thanks her mom: 'I didn't know how many prayers she sent up to heaven for me'

description: Hezbollah launched a ballistic missile at Tel Aviv early Wednesday, after Israel carried out strikes on Lebanon that killed hundreds of people and the militants fired rockets across northern Israel.
title: Hezbollah fires missile at Tel Aviv after heavy Israeli strikes on Lebanon

description: Threats and violence against inspectors have caused the U.S. to suspend inspections in the past. California growers question Mexico's inspectors would be better equipped to withstand the pressure.
title: U.S. to hand over pest inspections of Mexican avocados to Mexico
